name: Solitaire Voyage Tripeaks Card
description:
Tri Peaks Classic Cards Games

It's high time to take a break and relax after a hard-working day!

Solitaire Voyage.

This is an amazing card game that in a blink of an eye puts you to the atmosphere of VIP voyage around the world. You will feel both the euphoria of a luxury journey and the excitement of card games.

- Enjoy colorful graphics and stunning views of challenging levels.
- Discover a huge number of bonuses and mechanics along the way.
- Accumulate and multiply all your reward with the safe.
- Visit all fabulous venues including romantic Paris, exciting Venice, scenic Courchevel and other spectacular places.

Download and Play Tripeaks in Solitaire Voyage NOW!

A luxury voyage is waiting for travellers and players who are ready to join a fascinating Solitaire Voyage around the world!
